{"id":580269,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/03/【立此存照】中国特色妇女节：只许正能量，不可/","date":"2018-03-08T07:54:33Z","modified":"2018-03-08T10:31:41Z","title":"【立此存照】中国特色妇女节：只许正能量，不可反骚扰","content":"<p><strong>【编者注】</strong>国际妇女节当天，女权活动人士创建的 <strong>#三八反骚扰#</strong> 话题页面却被关闭，发表涉及《中国女记者性职场骚扰状况调查报告》内容的微博也被删除，与“me too”和反性骚扰有关的话题页面都面临着严格审查。</p>\n<p>与此同时，官媒则报道了“女民工穿汉服过三八节”等“正能量”内容，网络上充斥着诸如“全班就一个女生，男生送她整套口红”之类的“宠爱”女性的内容。甚至还出现了用“处置非正常上访事件1000余起、涉事群众7000余人”的<strong>维稳成果</strong>来“庆祝”国际三八妇女节的四川绵阳特巡警账号。</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_580271\" style=\"width: 535px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/三八反骚扰2-e1520483501525.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-580271\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/三八反骚扰2-e1520483501525.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"525\" height=\"374\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/三八反骚扰2-e1520483501525.jpg 1210w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/三八反骚扰2-e1520483501525-300x213.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/三八反骚扰2-e1520483501525-768x546.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/三八反骚扰2-e1520483501525-1024x729.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 525px) 100vw, 525px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"color: #808080\">微博截图</span></p></div>\n<blockquote><p>@七隻小怪獸：刚#三八反骚扰# 已被删。妇女节快乐祝我们永不遗忘，永不放弃对性别平等的争取，面对暴力和歧视永不沉默，那些对删除标签的穷追不舍阻挡不了坚强独立的女性们的勇敢发声，#米兔不能忘#此刻我愿邀你与我#三八高唱女人之歌#“你可愿和我一样【为权利抗争到老，打破沉重的枷锁，找回女人的力量&#8211;这才是妇女节的意义】为了自由，尊严，平等，自我赋予的力量，妇女节快乐</p></blockquote>\n<p><strong>截至发稿时，微博#三八反骚扰#话题已被删除，</strong>点击话题页面后会出现如下提示：</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_580275\" style=\"width: 410px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/IMG_4161.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-580275\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/IMG_4161.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\" height=\"682\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/IMG_4161.jpg 640w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/IMG_4161-176x300.jpg 176w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/IMG_4161-600x1024.jpg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"color: #808080\">点击“三八反骚扰”话题页面后显示话题不存在；微博截图</span></p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_580270\" style=\"width: 410px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/三八反骚扰1.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-580270\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/三八反骚扰1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\" height=\"712\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/三八反骚扰1.jpg 719w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/三八反骚扰1-169x300.jpg 169w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/三八反骚扰1-575x1024.jpg 575w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"color: #808080\">微博截图来自用户 @戳沙丁鱼</span></p></div>\n<blockquote><p><strong>相关阅读：中国数字空间｜</strong><strong><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/space/%E5%A5%B3%E6%9D%83%E4%B8%BB%E4%B9%89\">女权主义</a></strong></p></blockquote>\n<p><strong>通过微博搜索可以找到不少带有 #我的反性骚扰宣言# 标签的内容，但在话题页面却只有一条微博：</strong></p>\n<div id=\"attachment_580286\" style=\"width: 510px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/我的反性骚扰宣言.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-580286\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/我的反性骚扰宣言.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"391\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/我的反性骚扰宣言.jpg 1610w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/我的反性骚扰宣言-300x235.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/我的反性骚扰宣言-768x601.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/我的反性骚扰宣言-1024x801.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"color: #808080\">#我的反性骚扰宣言# 微博话题页面内容被过滤；网页截图</span></p></div>\n<p>同样地，<strong>虽然微博上有使用了 #米兔不能忘# 标签的微博，但话题页面却未能显示任何内容</strong>：</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_580287\" style=\"width: 510px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/米兔不能忘.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-580287\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/米兔不能忘.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"334\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/米兔不能忘.jpg 1484w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/米兔不能忘-300x201.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/米兔不能忘-768x513.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/米兔不能忘-1024x685.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"color: #808080\">#米兔不能忘#微博话题页面未能显示任何内容；网页截图</span></p></div>\n<h2>与此同时：</h2>\n<div id=\"attachment_580272\" style=\"width: 535px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/三八妇女节1.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-580272\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/三八妇女节1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"525\" height=\"413\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/三八妇女节1.jpg 1214w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/三八妇女节1-300x236.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/三八妇女节1-768x605.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/三八妇女节1-1024x806.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 525px) 100vw, 525px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"color: #808080\">微博截图</span></p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_580273\" style=\"width: 535px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/三八妇女节2.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-580273\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/三八妇女节2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"525\" height=\"377\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/三八妇女节2.jpg 1206w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/三八妇女节2-300x215.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/三八妇女节2-768x551.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/三八妇女节2-1024x735.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 525px) 100vw, 525px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"color: #808080\">微博截图</span></p></div>\n<blockquote><p>2017年全年，她们共参与规范处置市委市政府非正常上访事件1000余起、涉事群众7000余人，有力维护了市委市政府的正常工作秩序。</p></blockquote>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">Today on <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/InternationalWomensDay?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#InternationalWomensDay</a>, we call on China to release all detained &amp; imprisoned women human rights defenders. </p>\n<p>The govt can start by releasing Li Xiaoling, Li Yuhan, Liu Ping, Liu Xia, Jia Lingmin, Wang Fang, Wang Jing, Wang Shurong. Learn more about these women (1/9) <a href=\"https://t.co/f2BGePDh0W\">pic.twitter.com/f2BGePDh0W</a></p>\n<p>&mdash; CHRD人权捍卫者 (@CHRDnet) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/CHRDnet/status/971572622482812929?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">March 8, 2018</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<p>更有甚者，<strong>前半段还在介绍妇女节的来历</strong>，过去妇女如何通过努力为自己争取权益，<strong>后半段却画风突变，成了“女性地位已经非常高”，无论年龄都需要被“宠爱”这一套</strong>：</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_580291\" style=\"width: 510px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/妇女节1-down-e1520494472566.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-580291\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/妇女节1-down-e1520494472566.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"615\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/妇女节1-down-e1520494472566.jpg 991w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/妇女节1-down-e1520494472566-244x300.jpg 244w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/妇女节1-down-e1520494472566-768x945.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/妇女节1-down-e1520494472566-832x1024.jpg 832w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"color: #808080\">画风突变的正能量视频画面</span></p></div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_580285\" style=\"width: 535px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/三八妇女节3-1.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-580285\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/三八妇女节3-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"525\" height=\"443\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/三八妇女节3-1.jpg 1212w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/三八妇女节3-1-300x253.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/三八妇女节3-1-768x648.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/三八妇女节3-1-1024x863.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 525px) 100vw, 525px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"color: #808080\">微博截图（马赛克为本站所加）</span></p></div>\n","author":980,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,19168,27949],"tags":[27200,33760,33799,26991,32411,18979,8616]}